  "description": {
    "zh": "那么，你想证明自己知道哪里能找到子弹吗？你知道能找到弹药有多重要。或许如果你能带给我特定的弹药包，我会考虑未来向你开放我们的顶级弹药库存...不过这是以后的事。\n\n现在我需要你带来一些 5.45x39mm 的子弹包，就这一种类型就行，现在需要的就是这些。",
    "en": "So, wanna prove that you know where to find ammo? You know how important it is to know where to get your ammo. I might consider opening our stock of top tier ammo to you in the future, if you manage to bring the specific rounds to me of course... But that is something for later.\n\nWhat I need from you now is to bring me a few ammo packs for 5.45x39mm ammo, bring me a few small boxes and a few large ones, that should be everything... for now."
  },
